Has a company gone quiet after a promising conversation? Silence can often be uncertainty in disguise.

During The Licensing Playbook LIVE, happening later today, we're covering the topic of ghosting.

Well discuss why it happens, how to restart the conversation while maintaining professionalism, and what you can do early on to reduce the likelihood of silence.

Join our conversation with Dana Knowles and Chad Brislawn as we share practical ways to keep the conversation moving forward.

Bring your questions well be answering them live!
